title: FC Vinnytsia
text:
FC Vinnytsia is a Ukrainian amateur <a href="association%20football">football</a> team from <a href="Vinnytsia">Vinnytsia</a>. The club competes in the Amateur Championship since 2013.
History.
The club was founded in 2010 as FC Derzhsluzhbovets-KFKS Vinnytsia and competed in regional competitions of <a href="Vinnytsia%20Oblast">Vinnytsia Oblast</a>.
In 2012 the club changed its name to FC Vinnytsia and in 2013 entered the national amateur competitions.
